                                    <locus from="1r"/>
                                    <title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="LIT6168ManifOfHab">Manifestation of the prophet <persName ref="PRS4914Habakkuk">Habakkuk</persName> at Qarṭasā
                                        (<date ref="ethiocal:Hedar3">3rd of Ḫǝdār</date>)</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                        <locus from="1ra"/><hi rend="rubric">አመ፡ ሠሉሰ፡ ለኅዳር፡</hi> 
                                        አስተርእዮቱ፡ ለአን<hi rend="rubric">ባቆም፡ ነቢይ፡ በአ</hi>ማን፡ በሃገረ፡ እንተ፡ ስ<hi rend="rubric">ማ፡ ቀርጠሳ፡ እንዘ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ አባ፡ አርሚስ፡ 
